### 3. CUSEXTMI / Custom Extension Table (storing mashup config)

Reference: `Quick-Price-Quote/src/app/features/home/services/app-settings.service.ts`

When reading mashup configuration from M3's custom extension table:
```typescript
const request: IMIRequest = {
  program: 'CUSEXTMI',
  transaction: 'LstFieldValue',
  record: {
    FILE: 'MASHUP-CFG',
    PK01: 'GLOBAL',
    PK02: 'FEATURE-KEY',
    PK03: 'SETTING-NAME',
  },
  maxReturnedRecords: 100,
  typedOutput: true,
  includeMetadata: true,
};
```

