### 5. GDIS Services (Framework-level services)

Reference: `Quick-Price-Quote/src/app/app.component.ts`

These services from `@gdis/api` are available in all projects — inject and use them as needed:

| Service | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `MessageService` | Show toast/message notifications to users |
| `TranslationService` | Translate keys using the Transloco integration |
| `UserService` | Get current logged-in M3 user info |
| `ThemeService` | Get/set the IDS theme |
| `LocaleService` | Handle M3 locale/language settings |
| `UrlService` | Build M3/API URLs |
| `DebugService` | Debug logging |
| `HeaderService` | Control the application header |
| `GdisStore` | Global GDIS state |
| `AnalyticService` | Analytics tracking |
| `SettingsService` | App-level settings |

Import from `'@gdis/api'`:
```typescript
import { MessageService, UserService, TranslationService, GdisStore } from '@gdis/api';
```

