### 6. Path Aliases (tsconfig paths)

All projects use these path aliases — always use them instead of relative paths:

| Alias | Resolves to |
|---|---|
| `@core/` | `src/app/core/` |
| `@shared/` | `src/app/shared/` |
| `@gdis/` | `src/app/gdis/` |
| `@environments/` | `src/environments/` |
| `@features/` | `src/app/features/` (if defined) |

