### 7. File Structure (mirroring existing projects)

```
src/app/
  core/
    enums/          ← App-wide enums
    models/         ← Store base class, shared models
    providers/      ← Angular providers
    services/       ← Global services (global.store.ts, system.service.ts, etc.)
    tokens/         ← Angular injection tokens (WINDOW, etc.)
    types/          ← Global TypeScript types/interfaces
    utils/          ← Utility functions
  features/
    <feature-name>/
      components/   ← Presentational components
      pages/        ← Routed page components
      services/     ← Feature-scoped services
      enums/        ← Feature enums
      i18n/         ← Transloco translation JSON files
      utils/        ← Feature utility functions
      <feature>.routes.ts
  shared/
    components/     ← Reusable components used across features
    services/       ← Shared services
    types/          ← Shared interfaces
  gdis/             ← GDIS framework integration layer
```

---

### 8. Translation (Transloco)

- Add `TranslocoDirective` to standalone component imports.
- Use `*transloco="let t"` in templates.
- Translation JSON files go in `features/<feature>/i18n/<lang>.json`.
- Use `TranslationService` from `@gdis/api` for programmatic access.

